# Keep the GitHub language bar representative of the actual engineering.
# The analysis notebook is mostly embedded cell output (JSON-encoded tables and
# plots), which Linguist counts by bytes and would otherwise report as ~80%
# "Jupyter Notebook". Mark notebooks as documentation so they're excluded from
# the repository language statistics; the Python source then dominates, which is
# an honest reflection of the codebase.
*.ipynb linguist-documentation
